source.data:
Feature: Character search on Wikipedia using an API

  Scenario Outline: Request the first five characters on Star Wars API and validate
  Given the user is on SW api requesting character id <number>
  When the user search on Wikipedia "<cName>"
  Then the user should be able to see the article page correctly displayed for "<cName>"

  Examples:
    | number | cName |
    | 1 | Luke Skywalker |
    | 2 | C-3PO |
    | 3 | R2-D2 |
    | 4 | Darth Vader |
    | 5 | Princess Leia |

Feature: Movie search on Wikipedia using an API

  Scenario: Request random movie on the Star Wars API and validate
  Given the user is on SW api requesting a random movie
  And the user search on Wikipedia that movie
  When the user click on edit link
  Then the user should be able to see the article title correctly displayed for that

feature.name: Movie search on Wikipedia using an API

scenario.name: Request random movie on the Star Wars API and validate

steps.text: the user is on SW api requesting a random movie
the user search on Wikipedia that movie
the user click on edit link
the user should be able to see the article title correctly displayed for that
